'''Vine-silk''' was used to make elegant clothing worn by [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]]. It was grown on [[Belsavis/Legends|Belsavis]]. An amount of vine-silk suitable for making a single dress could cost up to 30% of a [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] economy.

